Plot: When Kimberly has a violent premonition of a highway pileup she blocks the freeway, keeping a few others meant to die, safe...Or are they? The survivors mysteriously start dying and it's up to Kimberly to stop it before she's next.
Title: Final Destination 2
Writer: J. Mackye Gruber (screenplay), Eric Bress (screenplay), J. Mackye Gruber (story), Eric Bress (story), Jeffrey Reddick (story), Jeffrey Reddick (characters)
Actors: Ali Larter, A.J. Cook, Michael Landes, David Paetkau
tomatoConsensus: This sequel is little more than an excuse to stage elaborate, gory scenes of characters getting killed off.
